# Real-message test fixtures captured from a live chat.db — never commit.
# Ignore the directory's *contents* (not the dir itself) so the negation below
# can re-include the one synthetic fixture; a `dir/` rule would stop git from
# descending and the `!` exception would never match.
src/__tests__/fixtures/*
# …except the fully synthetic, no-real-data sample fixture used by CI
!src/__tests__/fixtures/edit-summary.sample.bin